Oil, Gas and Consumable Fuels

Company Overview of Petroleum Marketers, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Petroleum Marketers, Inc., through its subsidiaries, distributes gasoline, diesel fuels, kerosene, home heating oils, bulk lubricants, and motor oils. It supplies and delivers petroleum products to commercial, dealer, governmental, and residential customers; provides for-hire transportation of petroleum products; and operates branded convenience stores. The company was incorporated in 1950 and is headquartered in Roanoke, Virginia. As of April 30, 2014, Petroleum Marketers, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Pinehurst Petroleum, LLC.


3000 Ogden RoadRoanoke, VA 24018United StatesFounded in 1950



