Vision & Mission

The Petroleum Marketers Association of America (PMAA) is a federation of 46 state and regional trade associations representing approximately 8,000 independent petroleum marketers nationwide. Take a look at who our member associations are or browse our site to learn more about us and the professionals we serve. 

Important Update


PMAA launches #FUELMATTERS – an innovative way to get people talking about the important issues around fuel! Learn more here.











PMAA Partners

PMAA sincerely thanks its partner companies for their support.



 






































































































 





