Other PMAA Publications
News From Capitol Hill
News From Capitol Hill is an e-publication that reports on breaking news from Capitol Hill. PMAA’s NFCH is distributed to our State Association members only.



PMAA Today
PMAA Today keeps members informed on association news and happenings. PMAA Today is distributed to our State Association members only.



Regulatory Report
Regulatory Reports provide important updates on regulatory actions and news. PMAA’s Regulatory Report is distributed to our State Association members only.



PMAA Journal
Our members and readers are approximately 8,000 independent petroleum marketers and convenience-store owners throughout the United States. Visit us online!






















