Welcome To Petroleum Marketing Group

Welcome to Petroleum Marketing Group (PMG). We are an established distributor and jobber of petroleum products & services throughout the Atlantic region of the United States. We own, operate, and/or supply over 1000 sites across Maryland, Virginia, Washington D.C., and New Jersey, and have an annual fuel volume of over 1 billion gallons..
PMG is an authorized distributor for the following brands:








