  About Us  


Since our founding in 2001, PMG has grown to become one of the leading jobbers and distributors of petroleum products and operators of convenience stores in the Mid-Atlantic region of the United States. Headquartered in Woodbridge VA, PMG services more than 850 locations, from Tidewater, Virginia to Northern New Jersey. The PMG team is made up of more than 1100 dedicated industry professionals with the common goal of providing excellent service to our customers.
 
PMG is an authorized distributor for Shell, Exxon, Mobil, BP, Sunoco, Citgo, Gulf, 76 and Crown brands and supplies non-branded petroleum products as well. We deliver over 1 billion gallons of petroleum on an annual basis. Since PMG’s establishment in 2001, the company has grown exponentially thanks to a well-planned expansion program, an experienced and knowledgeable staff, and unique financial abilities.
 
Today PMG is a full-service provider in the industry. The Company provides its clients with a variety of services, including:


Gas station design and C-store design
Site engineering
Construction
Project financing
Environmental management
Fuel supply and delivery
Convenience store operations including 7-Eleven, Marketplace,
Corner Mart and Circle-K
Food service operations including Dunkin’ Donuts and Subway
Station maintenance management
Management training and support
Back office accounting support
Transportation – Quest Transport (link)
PMG WineRacks (link)








  


