Mission

Mission: To be a premier petroleum and convenience retail and wholesale organization, in order to achieve profitability and growth for our dealers, company and our people!
Community
PMG has a commitment to give back in the communities in which we operate. One way we do this is through a balanced focus on alternative energies such as biofuel and other clean-burning fuels. This is achieved through strategic alliances with leaders and forward thinkers in our industry and communities. Over the past few years we have also directly contributed over a quarter million dollars to the Paralympics, St. Judes Children’s Hospital, The Wounded Warriors, and the Muscular Dystrophy Association (MDA). We understand that our employees and customers are the driving force behind our success as a company and we take pride in making a positive impact in the communities we share.
Our Vision

Remain a long term premier marketing organization
Employee growth and profitability
Company growth and profitability
Customer focus-they make all this possible!






