Business Opportunities

At PMG we are constantly seeking out new & innovative ways to improve our business. PMG offers a wide range of services as a jobber and distributor of petroleum products and as an operator of wholesale and retail convenience stores and national food service brands. It is our goal to provide our customers with efficient, reliable, and high quality service. If you have a complimentary business or product offering to help us achieve these goals, please Contact Us.
 
In addition to our company operations, PMG has a large network of channel partners (dealers) in the Mid-Atlantic region and across New Jersey. If you are interested in partnering with PMG as a Dealer, we can provide you with branded or unbranded opportunities. Our brands include Shell, Exxon, Mobil, BP, Sunoco, Citgo, Gulf, 76 and Crown. PMG has an excellent track record of implementing branded supplier programs as well as developing custom retail programs to support our dealer network. Our territory managers work closely with our dealers across the region to ensure their success.
 
If you have interest in becoming a Dealer, please complete and return the application below:
 
Download application Form (PDF)
Real Estate
 
PMG has grown through strategic acquisitions of retail petroleum sites. We currently own and supply over 850 sites and are continuing to expand our footprint. If you are interested in buying or selling potential retail properties, please contact Jeff Bucaro of the Real Estate department on our Contact Page. If you have a property that you would like to develop into a modern service station, we can help with that as well. You can contact us with any additional questions or comments.





